data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom house with a covered front porch! Walk into the large great room that boasts an abundance of natural light. The spacious kitchen features TWO pantries, a breakfast bar & all appliances stay & it opens to the dining area! The primary bedroom offers TWO closets and a bathroom with a walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms share a bathroom. Bonus room with hot tub offering relaxation and entertainment options all year round. A sunroom with large windows provides an ideal space to unwind while enjoying the view of the outdoors. An oversized 2-car garage with a workshop area & a carport providing ample parking & storage options. Relax outside in the large fenced-in backyard that features a firepit.
